caption.title: Analysis of variance of the effects of OA and T and their interaction on absolute flows and transfer efficiency between successive trophic levels of the food web.
caption.p: Significant differences are indicated with asterisks, with *: p < 0.05, **: p < 0.01, and ***: p < 0.001. OA, elevated CO 2; T, elevated temperature.
